    "D. Integrating LLMs and EKGsThe integration of Large Language Models (LLMs) and Knowledge Graphs (KGs) aims to combine their strengths, with LLMs excelling in language prediction and KGs providing structured, factual knowledge [58].",
    "However, LLMs alone lack grounding in facts, while KGs struggle with natural language nuances.",
    "Alam et al. [59] improve KG embeddings for graph completion, addressing issues like neglecting textual data.",
    "Pan et al. [60] explore strategies for integrating LLMs with KGs to enhance LLM inference.",
    "Despite progress, challenges like frequent updates and generalization to unseen data persist [61]."
  ],
